---
title: Chive Chicken and Wild Rice with Buttery Carrots
description: A classic 1,2,3 meal is sometimes all you need to please the whole family. Buttery carrots, savoury wild rice and chive chicken are what you'll find in this elevated weeknight chicken dinner!
